<emphasis id="55CDEF554013466DFCFC80C1EA84B592" box="[809,953,1514,1535]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="1263">
<typeStatus id="B8028DE54013466DFCFC80C1EA63B592" box="[809,862,1514,1535]" pageId="11" pageNumber="1263">Type</typeStatus>
species:
</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="A0B948C44013466DFC1080C1EC64B592" authority="Slabber, 1769" authorityName="Slabber" authorityYear="1769" box="[965,1369,1513,1535]" class="Malacostraca" family="Haustoriidae" genus="Haustorius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="11" pageNumber="1263" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="arenarius">
<emphasis id="55CDEF554013466DFC1080C1ED84B592" box="[965,1209,1514,1535]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="1263">Haustorius arenarius</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="03284EB64013466DFB1580C2EC64B592" author="Slabber M" box="[1216,1369,1513,1535]" pageId="11" pageNumber="1263" refId="ref10860" refString="Slabber M. 1769. Natuurkundige verlustigingen, behelzende microscopise waarneemingen van de in- en uitlandse wateren land-dieren. Haarlem: J. Bosch." type="book" year="1769">Slabber, 1769</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="670633474013466DFCFC8303EA8FB6D5" blockId="11.[809,1425,1576,1720]" pageId="11" pageNumber="1263">
<emphasis id="55CDEF554013466DFCFC8303EA9EB650" box="[809,931,1576,1597]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="1263">Diagnosis:</emphasis>
Large haustoriids (
<quantity id="A0419EA24013466DFB498303EC30B650" box="[1180,1293,1576,1598]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.05" metricValueMax="1.6" metricValueMin="0.5" pageId="11" pageNumber="1263" unit="mm" value="10.5" valueMax="16.0" valueMin="5.0">5–16 mm</quantity>
). Maxilla 2 outer lobe narrow and lanceolate, more than twice size of inner lobe. Pleon overhanging urosome; epimeron 3 smooth, ventrally curved (without hook). Telson cleft emarginate.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="670633474013466DFCFC83C9ED2EB73E" blockId="11.[809,1425,1761,1875]" pageId="11" pageNumber="1263">
<emphasis id="55CDEF554013466DFCFC83C9EAE6B69A" box="[809,987,1762,1783]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="1263">Known species:</emphasis>
